HEADWORD: legalese
<hw>legalese</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A style of writing or speaking
heavily emphasizing the abstruse technical vocabulary of the law, to the
point where a speech or document may be incomprehensible to
non-specialists.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>legalisation</ent>⟦br⟧
